Uses of Class
hc.server.ui.MenuItem

  • Packages that use MenuItem 
    Package Description
    hc.server.ui  

    • Uses of MenuItem in hc.server.ui

      Methods in hc.server.ui that return MenuItem 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      MenuItem ProjectContext.getMenuItemBy(String scheme, String elementID)
      for example, to get menu item "cmd://myCommand",
      the scheme is "CMD_SCHEME", and element ID is "myCommand",

      if in project level, search item from list of project level.
      if in session level, search item from total list of project level and session level.
      MenuItem ProjectContext.getMenuItemFromProjectLevel(int position)
      return position item from list of project level.
      MenuItem ProjectContext.getMenuItemFromSessionLevel(int position)
      return position item from list of session level.
      MenuItem ProjectContext.removeMenuItemFromProjectLevel(int position)
      remove position from list of project level.
      MenuItem ProjectContext.removeMenuItemFromSessionLevel(int position)
      remove position from list of session level.
      Methods in hc.server.ui with parameters of type MenuItem 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void ProjectContext.addMenuItem(MenuItem item)
      add a mobile/client menu item for project or session at run-time.

      if in project level, add item to list of project level.
      if in session level, add item to list of session level.
      boolean ProjectContext.addMenuItemToProjectLevel(MenuItem item, int position)
      it is equals with ProjectContext.insertMenuItemToProjectLevel(MenuItem, int).
      boolean ProjectContext.addMenuItemToSessionLevel(MenuItem item, int position)
      it is equals with ProjectContext.insertMenuItemToSessionLevel(MenuItem, int).
      void ProjectContext.insertMenuItem(MenuItem item)
      it is equals with ProjectContext.addMenuItem(MenuItem).
      boolean ProjectContext.insertMenuItemToProjectLevel(MenuItem item, int position)
      inserts the mobile/client menu item at a given position into project list.
      boolean ProjectContext.insertMenuItemToSessionLevel(MenuItem item, int position)
      inserts the mobile/client menu item at a given position into session list.
      boolean ProjectContext.removeMenuItem(MenuItem item)
      removes the specified menu item.
